<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l13"><expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / cʒü vns vnd <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> vns vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jr rede <expan>geneinand<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l14"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>hör<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>beſehe<ex>n</ex></expan> ob man gütlıch wege <expan>darvnt<ex>er</ex></expan> vinden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l15">müge / . vnd wer es / daʒ ſie in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit als vvir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l16"><expan>Lantg<ex>ra</ex>f<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Johanſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒü vns kömen / . was </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l17">vvir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vvıllen <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> getün <expan>mocht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l18"><expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir tün / Alſo daʒ ewr gnad ſehen ſolt / daʒ ſie ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l19">etwas genieſſen <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vvan wo etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>Sup<ex>ra</ex></expan> $ . </ab>
